title: Golden Rod
overview: Ever had that secret agent fantasy? Flying to exotic countries... bedding mysterious women. Well, Horizon DVD presents the ultimate in sex, crime and adventure. Rebecca Wild heads up an all star cast as a luscious femme fatale with a taste for the high life. So if you like your sex hot (D.P.s, anal) and your martini shaken, not stirred, Golden Rod is one movie you can bond with!
